SUMMARY: Building with Mistral: Open\, Powerful\, and Ready to Scale
DESCRIPTION:Data Science Raleigh\nExplore how to develop and deploy Enterprise AI applications with Mistral AI in this practical\, insight-driven session. We’ll walk through Mistral’s full model spectrum—from Large to Small—and how to select the right capabilities for your specific use case.\n\nYou’ll get an introduction to Mistral AI Studio and learn how to begin building\, customizing\, and managing AI applications with speed and control. The session will also cover flexible deployment pathways\, including serverless\, cloud\, on-premise\, Cloud-VPC\, and dedicated instances—so you can align infrastructure with enterprise requirements.\n\n**What You’ll Learn:**\n\n🔹 **Model Selection Strategy:** Understand the Large-to-Small model spectrum and when to use each.\n🔹 **Application Development:** Build and tailor AI applications in Mistral AI Studio.\n🔹 **Flexible Deployment Options:** Compare serverless\, cloud\, on-prem\, VPC\, and dedicated setups.\n🔹 **Production Best Practices:** Apply practical guidance to move AI projects into enterprise-scale production.\n\nGain the clarity and tools needed to take AI initiatives from experimentation to reliable\, production-ready systems.\n\n**[Register here](https://hubs.ly/Q045pnzM0)**
