SUMMARY:Plug & Play: Live AI Workflows in Action
DESCRIPTION:Data Science Raleigh\nForget static demos and slide decks. Plug & Play Sessions are all about showing\, not telling. In this hands-on webinar series\, you'll see tech leaders walk through their AI product in real time\, highlighting exactly how it works in the wild: setup\, workflows\, integrations\, all in just 30 minutes.\n\nBuilt on the momentum of our AI Demo Day format\, Plug & Play goes deeper. Presenters slow down and dig in: demonstrating usability\, showing off speed to value\, and guiding attendees through common real-world scenarios. It’s a rare opportunity to see how tools behave under actual conditions\, not just polished slides.\n\nExpect 2–3 hours of back-to-back\, engaging walkthroughs. Attendees are encouraged to click along live\, ask questions\, and walk away with more than awareness—usable knowledge.\n\n**Key Takeaways:**\n\n1️⃣ **Real Product Experience:** See full workflows in motion—not just the highlights.\n\n2️⃣ **Usability in Focus:** Evaluate ease of use\, integration paths\, and how quickly value is delivered.\n\n3️⃣ **Interactive Learning:** Follow along live and get answers as you go.\n\n4️⃣ **Depth Over Demos:** A deeper understanding of how AI tools actually fit into your stack.\n\n**[Register here](https://hubs.ly/Q042c9tg0)**
