SUMMARY:From AI to ROI: Turning Pilots Into Scalable Impact
DESCRIPTION:Data Science Raleigh\nEvery enterprise has its share of AI proof-of-concepts—many promising\, few enduring. This webinar goes beyond the hype to explore what it actually takes to move from experimental AI pilots to sustained\, enterprise-wide value. We’ll dig into the operational\, organizational\, and architectural levers that help AI investments move out of the sandbox and into the business mainstream.\n\nThrough expert discussion and real-world examples\, we’ll explore the friction points that stall scaling efforts—and what forward-thinking leaders are doing to overcome them. If you're leading or influencing AI adoption in your organization\, this session is about turning progress into performance.\n\n**Key Takeaways:**\n\n1️⃣ **Real Product Experience:** See full workflows in motion—not just the highlights.\n\n2️⃣ **Operational Readiness:** What’s required in terms of data infrastructure\, governance\, and cross-functional collaboration to support scaled AI.\n\n3️⃣ **Organizational Design:** How roles\, incentives\, and workflows evolve when AI becomes a core operating capability.\n\n4️⃣ **Sustaining Value:** Strategies for continuous iteration\, observability\, and measuring long-term ROI from AI investments.\n\n**[Register here](https://hubs.ly/Q041vh4c0)**
