SUMMARY:Agentic AI in Action: 10-Minute Demo Spotlights from the Frontier Q2
DESCRIPTION:Data Science Raleigh\nExplore the real-world impact of Agentic AI in our fast-paced\, insight-packed virtual showcase. Each 10-minute session features a live demo from a leading innovator in the Agentic AI space—highlighting practical applications\, dynamic workflows\, and tangible business outcomes.\n\nThis isn't just another pitch session. It’s a curated look at how agent-based systems are driving intelligent automation\, adaptive planning\, and cross-functional orchestration across industries. You’ll meet the minds behind these technologies and see firsthand how they’re redefining what's possible in enterprise AI.\n\n**What You'll Learn:**\n\n1️⃣ **Autonomous Workflows:** See how agentic systems plan\, coordinate\, and execute complex tasks across tools and teams.\n\n2️⃣ **Dynamic Decisioning:** Explore examples of contextual reasoning\, goal alignment\, and memory-enhanced agents in action.\n\n3️⃣**Practical Integration:** Understand what it takes to embed agentic AI into your stack—without overhauling everything.\n\nEngage live with founders and builders shaping the future of autonomous enterprise solutions.\n\nYou’re short on time but deep on curiosity. This format respects both—cutting straight to the tech and the teams behind it. No filler\, no fluff. Just signal.\n\n**[Register here](https://hubs.ly/Q042cVj20)**
